# SWAP test using Fredkin (CSWAP) gate
#
# The SWAP test estimates |<psi|phi>|^2 using:
#   1. ancilla qubit in |+>  (H on qubit 0)
#   2. CSWAP(ancilla=0, qubit1, qubit2)
#   3. H on ancilla again
#   4. Measure ancilla: P(0) = (1 + |<psi|phi>|^2) / 2
#
# Here psi = phi = |0> so overlap = 1 -> P(ancilla=0) = 1 (always 0).
# Initialize: qubit 0 = ancilla, qubit 1 = |psi>, qubit 2 = |phi>
INIT 3 1
# Ancilla into |+>
H 0
# |psi> = |0>, |phi> = |0> (already ground state)
# CSWAP
CSWAP 0 1 2
# H on ancilla
H 0
# Measure ancilla
MEASURE 0 0
DISPLAY
